msgid "Automatic password hiding"
msgstr "自动隐藏密码"

#: src/frontend/keysclicks-window.c:996
msgid ""
"On (PRO) — passwords are hidden automatically in password fields. This "
"module is still in development."
msgstr "开启（PRO）— 在密码字段中自动隐藏密码。此模块仍在开发中。"

#: src/frontend/keysclicks-window.c:998
msgid ""
"PRO — in development. Automatic hiding ships with the PRO add-on; the manual "
"\"Hide keys\" toggle/shortcut works now."
msgstr ""
"PRO — 开发中。自动隐藏功能将随 PRO 附加组件提供；手动的“Hide keys”开关/快捷键"
"现已可用。"

